{"tid":1857213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽］假如今日政府有任何讓步，加強封關，都係醫護罷工爭取番嚟，即使柒婆一定唔撚認","createTime":"2020-02-02T05:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:56:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"efe05873e627558a94bda1e333d96710b6aea4ff","tid":1857213,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"睇林正財口風<br />\n有可能再做野<br />\n<br />\n777故意唔見工會<br />\n有任何讓步都一定spin成佢開完會聽專家講既英明決定<br />\n同罷工冇關<br />\n但以佢性格，肯定又鬥氣做唔足<br />\n扮冇跪（好似暫緩咁）<br />\n<br />\n佢想否定罷工既正當性<br />\n如果真罷，方便日後清算<br />\n唔罷，又可以講成自己成功平息事件<br />\n<br />\n所以所有文宣<br />\n一定要指出罷工成功迫使政府讓步哩點（假如一陣政府真係讓步）"},{"pid":"3e57db3a1d5793eccc07e8b5e5416742991c9adc","tid":1857213,"uid":55317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"似係開完個乜春委員會扮探討完<br />\n<br />\n之後再宣布再封部分口岸<br />\n<br />\n會話唔係因為醫護罷工 而家之前成效不足所以再封<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好中計<br />\n<br />\n全靠醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7947a5832026c05111bedbef9f920da76776f59e","tid":1857213,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e57db3a1d5793eccc07e8b5e5416742991c9adc","tid":1857213,"uid":55317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"似係開完個乜春委員會扮探討完<br />\n<br />\n之後再宣布再封部分口岸<br />\n<br />\n會話唔係因為醫護罷工 而家之前成效不足所以再封<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好中計<br />\n<br />\n全靠醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"醫管局范紅鈴即係羅范阿哥<br />\n紅到出血<br />\n事後一定想玩批鬥清算"},{"pid":"b5a200e51cb9521e62f579b7376c987f2e979897","tid":1857213,"uid":269301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:38:01.000Z",